# OmP fork context — track curated artifacts, exclude ephemeral OMC tooling state
# (HUD cache, session dumps, ralph state, etc. that may leak in from OMC usage)
.omc/state/*
!.omc/state/current-task.md
!.omc/state/prev-task.md

